  <brief_title>Trial of Effect of High-frequency Transcranial Magnetic Stimulation in the Management of Borderline Personality Disorder</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Sham-controlled Trial of Effect of High-frequency Transcranial Magnetic Stimulation in the Management of Borderline Personality Disorder Patients</official_title>
